Heather Lind https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heather_Lind 0 Heather Lind (born March 22, 1983) is an American actress. She is known for her portrayal of Anna Strong in the AMC series Turn: Washington's Spies. She is the twin sister of actress Christina Bennett Lind.
